{"tid":2127511,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"邵家臻不獲浸大續約擬上訴：殺了公雞也阻不了天亮","createTime":"2020-07-27T11:05:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T11:15:01.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bdaa0d665e245c259c3bc054aa61ecd969802653","tid":2127511,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:05:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200727/LMI3XBQOEGFIYWQIC36IG2ZAFM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200727%2FLMI3XBQOEGFIYWQIC36IG2ZAFM%2F&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpaooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=0bdd02a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200727%2FLMI3XBQOEGFIYWQIC36IG2ZAFM%2F&h=7745dd88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200727/LMI3XBQOEGFIYWQIC36IG2ZAFM/</a><br />\n<br />\n佔中九子之一、身兼浸大社工系講師的立法會社福界議員邵家臻指，今早約11時半接獲浸大人事部主管電郵，指其續約申請不獲批准，但未有列明原因。他今午在政府總部外的「命運自主台」位置舉行記者會，他直言解除合約並非意外之事，但對於浸大校方的刁難及打壓仍然感到憤怒，又指會向校方要求上訴，並希望可以獲得浸大校方的會議紀錄，重申「即使係殺了公雞也阻不了天亮」。"},{"pid":"57c4c594aa8e1765d0ba909a80300f780372a4b3","tid":2127511,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:15:01.000Z","msg":"雙失中年又有病"}]}